Magic and sorcery are different. Magic is what gods use, like in fairy
tales, while sorcery is what humans use.

Magic is a word that represents an abstract concept that encompasses
nature.
Everything is made up of physical laws and natural laws.

Understanding the laws of physics leads to the manipulation of
sorcery.

However, if there is a way to manipulate the very laws of nature, it
could be called nothing other than sorcery.
By the way... we're not in class right now.
Oh, so sorcery is what was invented to use magic.
I will also become a court sorceress like Lady Anastasia someday.

This is the Magic Academy... um, Anastasia-sama, you know about it,
right?

Anastasia-sama, who graduated at the top of this school, is our role
model.

I will someday surpass you. I will show everyone who the true genius
is.

The exams here are not only difficult in practical skills, but also in
paper tests...
To weave powerful sorcery, advanced knowledge is required...
In order to become a sorcerer, you must also be able to study.

In order to use sorcery, you need to develop intricate formulas of
physical laws in your mind...
People who can use powerful magic are often intelligent, that's why.

I'm so worried about the next exam because if my grades are bad, I
might get expelled from this school...

There are some students who cannot be contacted... Our school is
strict when it comes to classes and exams, but these students are not
the type to run away because of something like that...
Are you Anastasia, the daughter of the chairman?

Please take care of the missing students in place of us inadequate
teachers.

I've heard various rumors about you in your capital. They say you're a
genius sorcerer.

I saw the thesis you left behind at this academy, and honestly, even
as a teacher, I was amazed.

To be able to find a missing student so easily... Truly, you are
amazing, Anastasia.

Even though you're still young, it's truly terrifying. I understand
why the students admire you.

There's a student who can't be reached. Maybe they ran away because
our school is strict?
Even the students we couldn't contact have returned...
So, we're going back to our normal school life again.

Teachers are desperately searching, but there are students who can't
be found... This is... an incident!!
It seems that the missing person case was resolved easily...
I still feel like there's something more...
You were fighting by my side!!
